    "description": "Pieter Both Village 是一款惊险的第三人称视角僵尸冒险游戏，将你带入毛里求斯传奇的皮特博斯山脚下一个偏远而诡异的村庄。游戏灵感来自一个令人毛骨悚然的毛里求斯民间传说，将你沉浸在一个神话与现实碰撞的世界中，过去不愿被埋葬。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/5358924d9d099a35349c018468eca944.poster.avif?t=1727696152\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/5358924d9d099a35349c018468eca944.webm?t=1727696152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/5358924d9d099a35349c018468eca944.mp4?t=1727696152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i>主要特色：[/b]</i>引人入胜的故事情节：揭开皮特博斯村诅咒背后的秘密。探索一个黑暗的故事，每一个线索都让你离解开这座诅咒之山的恐怖秘密更近一步。<br><br><strong><i>僵尸生存：</i></strong>面对不死的村民和生物！运用你的智慧和武器，在危机四伏的世界中生存下来。<br><br><strong><i>氛围探索：</i></strong>探索各种令人毛骨悚然的环境，包括荒凉的村庄、阴森的皮特博斯山、笼罩在神秘中的古老寺庙，以及隐藏着黑暗秘密的广袤甘蔗田。每个场景都经过精心设计，让你在拼凑村庄悲惨过去的过程中时刻保持警惕。<br><br><strong><i>挑战性谜题：</i></strong>发现新区域并揭示隐藏的秘密。每解开一个谜题，你就离解除诅咒更近一步。<br><br><strong><i>毛里求斯民间传说：</i></strong>沉浸在受当地传说启发的独特背景中。探索包含传说中的渡渡鸟和宝藏在内的毛里求斯历史元素，这些都融入了游戏叙事之中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/26c211b2ddee5b1132b40cf65c4a0af0.poster.avif?t=1727696152\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/26c211b2ddee5b1132b40cf65c4a0af0.webm?t=1727696152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/26c211b2ddee5b1132b40cf65c4a0af0.mp4?t=1727696152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>引人入胜的故事情节，伴随不断变化的环境<br>以动作为主的冒险，包含枪械和徒手战斗系统<br>互动机制，包括跳跃、跨越、蹲伏和拾取物品<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/35a9a68e06521d820a0faf192810a0ed.poster.avif?t=1727696152\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/35a9a68e06521d820a0faf192810a0ed.webm?t=1727696152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099320/extras/35a9a68e06521d820a0faf192810a0ed.mp4?t=1727696152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
